{"tid":597670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【MH370之謎】用Google Earth追蹤 澳工程師聲稱搵到客機殘骸","createTime":"2018-03-19T00:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T02:44:44.000Z","uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52c79bab1023529c2cd221949aa04811ace2578a","tid":597670,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:19:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180319/57965563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F57965563&d=i42euQ6IMgmSN7yCN6aTHQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=397e1c3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F57965563&h=0b9aeafb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180319/57965563</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬航MH370客機失蹤四周年，機身殘骸一直未尋獲，澳洲一名機械工程師近日聲稱用Google Earth發現殘骸位置。<br />\n<br />\n業餘空難調查專家麥克馬洪（Peter McMahon）聲稱，殘骸位於印度洋西南部毛里裘斯（Mauritius）龍德島（Round Island）以南16公里的海底。搜索人員從未搜索過這裏。<br />\n<br />\n麥克馬洪展示圖片，指水底隱然出現機身及前端的輪廓。他表示已將資料交給澳洲運輸安全局（ATSB），對方亦表示不能完全排除那是飛機。<br />\n<br />\n麥克馬洪將他的「陰謀論」再推深一層，認為美國拒絕搜索該海域，又指美國派過四名調查員到澳洲，參與MH370失蹤的調查，但認為他們隱瞞重要資料，因為殘骸滿佈子彈孔，「所以美國人不想有人發現殘骸，而又開另一次研訊」。<br />\n<br />\n馬航編號MH370的波音777客機，2014年3月8日載着239名乘客及機組人員，原定由馬來西亞吉隆坡前往北京，卻在起飛約40分鐘後與控制塔失聯，不知所終。<br />\n<br />\nMH370失蹤近17個月後，印度洋法屬留尼汪島（La R&eacute;union）海灘出現疑似客機機翼殘骸及一件破爛行李，美國調查員及大馬官員都「幾乎肯定」，屬於MH370所屬的波音777客機機款。馬來西亞和澳洲官員2016年證實，在毛里求斯東北部海岸尋獲的機翼殘骸，屬於MH370。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞、中國及澳洲在南印度洋12萬平方公里範圍內展開搜索行動，耗資達1.6億美元（12.5億港元），始終找不到機身殘骸，去年1月在一無所獲下結束行動。"},{"pid":"f58f27b29a929a3c59048a6c73ed59f22a0da024","tid":597670,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0e11242d3d227f9e8f1ec0ce9f1a8a08ce34d86","tid":597670,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180319/large/1521403637_e68a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180319%2Flarge%2F1521403637_e68a.jpg&h=9ddbeaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會唔會仲未沉到底啊"},{"pid":"6c290a6d43bf00ebfc62b2ab7c25dbd1572f64a8","tid":597670,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:23:34.000Z","msg":"業餘空難調查專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱檸茶多冰既朋友"},{"pid":"c0cea28e2ce65aa1b4ff12b746108f7d070aae05","tid":597670,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"之前澳洲定唔知邊到唔係話無限期搜索直至揾到為止架咩？"},{"pid":"d8511cccb53adde0b7302749ebdf8f26f99f09ae","tid":597670,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0e11242d3d227f9e8f1ec0ce9f1a8a08ce34d86","tid":597670,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180319/large/1521403637_e68a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180319%2Flarge%2F1521403637_e68a.jpg&h=9ddbeaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會唔會仲未沉到底啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"會咁完整？"},{"pid":"a5f135c87c1673dbf657b2da8c8465e7dd9bed15","tid":597670,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"去左平行時空啦"},{"pid":"38e74f2d963a012beecce3e835d94d8536bf0002","tid":597670,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a5f135c87c1673dbf657b2da8c8465e7dd9bed15","tid":597670,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"去左平行時空啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/103558_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\